Description: A collection of associations and mapping to DBpedia entities. Currently consisting of 780000 human associations from the Edinburgh Associative Thesaurus (as RDF) and a verified mapping of 790 strong distinct associations (corresponding to ~25000 human associations) to DBpedia entities.See https://w3id.org/associations for more information.
